ShellFeatures -[#1565C0]-> RuntimeGeneration
ShellFeatures -[#1565C0]-> Catalog
ShellFeatures -[#1565C0]-> SharedApi

ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> ConversationUI
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> RoleplayUI
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> GameSurface
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> SharedModeUI
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> RuntimeGeneration
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> WorldState
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> Visuals
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> Catalog
ModeSurface -[#1565C0]-> SharedFrontend

ConversationUI -[#1565C0]-> ChatEngine
RoleplayUI -[#1565C0]-> RoleplayEngine
GameSurface -[#1565C0]-> GameEngine

ConversationUI -[#1565C0]-> SharedModeUI
RoleplayUI -[#1565C0]-> SharedModeUI
GameSurface -[#1565C0]-> SharedModeUI

ConversationUI -[#1565C0]-> RuntimeGeneration
RoleplayUI -[#1565C0]-> WorldState
GameSurface -[#1565C0]-> WorldState
GameSurface -[#1565C0]-> Visuals

RuntimeGeneration -[#1565C0]-> EngineGeneration
RuntimeGeneration -[#1565C0]-> SharedApi
WorldState -[#1565C0]-> SharedApi
Visuals -[#1565C0]-> SharedApi
Catalog -[#1565C0]-> SharedApi

EngineGeneration --> GenerationCore
EngineGeneration --> AgentRuntime
EngineGeneration --> Ports
ChatEngine --> EngineGeneration
RoleplayEngine --> EngineGeneration
GameEngine --> EngineGeneration
ChatEngine --> Contracts
RoleplayEngine --> Contracts
GameEngine --> Contracts
GenerationCore --> Contracts
Ports --> Contracts

SharedApi -[#1565C0,dotted]-> Ports : implements capability ports
SharedApi -[#1565C0]-> CommandRegistry : invoke/listen boundary
CommandRegistry --> Commands
Commands --> ImportModules
Commands --> RustStorage
Commands --> RustAssets
Commands --> RustLlm
Commands --> RustIntegrations
Commands --> RustSecurity
